Mr Kewley also alleges that people from other tour groups claim to have seen an apparition that resembles Read, who was behind bars from 20 to 38 years of age.

Read, who's been convicted of a long list of crimes including assault, arson, armed robbery, kidnapping, firearm offences and impersonating a police officer, died of liver cancer in October last year.

